{"tid":843714,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"傳施丹致電摩佬澄清冇搞鬼","createTime":"2018-10-01T10:57:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T13:35:27.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"27be82a2f42deae38ff2de9bbd9f6ee38e9c13bd","tid":843714,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T10:57:25.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=wxCBMOCrh%2F4zoxv4IeR4H%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=c200f619\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】施丹被爆致電予摩連奴，究竟所為何事？<br />\n<br />\n曼聯領隊摩連奴的帥位岌岌可危，盛傳在今夏離開皇家馬德里後一直未有落班的主帥施丹（Zinedine Zidane）是接手的大熱人選。<br />\n<br />\n英國《太陽報》周一爆料指，施丹為怕摩佬以為自己在他背後搞小動作，最近親身致電，向對方解釋只是其經理人問自己有沒有興趣執教紅魔。兩人曾在皇馬共事，在2010年摩佬執教該西甲豪門時，施丹就以特別顧問、及後的體育總監身份，跟對方緊密合作。<br />\n<br />\n雖然獲施丹友誼式的來電，但肯定令摩佬壓力更大，因為證明了曼聯管理層正在尋找繼任人選，準備好辭退他。<br />\n<br />\n曼聯最近3場不勝，上場英超作客韋斯咸以1:3落敗，一般認為若他們於周二歐聯主場鬥華倫西亞未能重返勝軌，摩佬就會下台。<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : Instagram圖片"},{"pid":"d16a4d6a33dceb85b832e9ab01b273ae239fe16a","tid":843714,"uid":16659,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T10:58:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://media.giphy.com/media/9DcxwUK4C4seesf9d0/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2F9DcxwUK4C4seesf9d0%2Fgiphy.gif&h=a430c83d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n救救Daddy吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41756224376613e4f76dd376dc98902173652cde","tid":843714,"uid":194062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T12:25:01.000Z","msg":"此地無銀三百兩"},{"pid":"132c3114a40249c7d00f3af3353f387316131d31","tid":843714,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T12:29:21.000Z","msg":"攞景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f4cf5f225f4f47d5d2388cccb67c2c1b93353e5","tid":843714,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike